1
00:02:00,798 --> 00:02:02,665
- I HAVE ERECTED A BARRIER.

2
00:02:02,698 --> 00:02:06,198
THOSE SERVANTS OF YOURS
MAY NOT ENTER.

3
00:02:09,731 --> 00:02:14,731
WITHOUT YOUR SOULS OF THE DEAD,
YOU REMAIN HELPLESS.

4
00:02:15,865 --> 00:02:19,931
KIKYO, WHAT CAN YOU
BE THINKING?

5
00:02:23,865 --> 00:02:25,465
THERE AT THE MOUNTAIN,

6
00:02:25,498 --> 00:02:27,065
WHERE THE MAGIC WAS BROKEN,

7
00:02:27,098 --> 00:02:30,031
WERE THE DEMONS
WHO WERE TO CREATE MY BODY.

8
00:02:30,065 --> 00:02:32,531
INUYASHA STUMBLED
ONTO THE SCENE,

9
00:02:32,565 --> 00:02:36,598
LURED BY THE MIASMA,
AND BEGAN TO DO BATTLE

10
00:02:36,631 --> 00:02:39,665
WITH THE ONE WHO WOULD WIN.

11
00:02:39,698 --> 00:02:42,898
THEN YOU APPEARED.

12
00:02:43,398 --> 00:02:46,365
[ROARING]

13
00:02:48,531 --> 00:02:50,865
YOUR ARROWS HAVE
THE POWER TO BREAK

14
00:02:50,898 --> 00:02:53,631
WHICHEVER SPELL YOU CHOOSE.

15
00:02:53,665 --> 00:02:57,898
AND YET, IF YOU WANTED TO
PREVENT THAT UNHOLY FUSION,

16
00:02:57,931 --> 00:03:00,798
YOU OUGHT TO HAVE AIMED
STRAIGHT FOR THE DEMON.

17
00:03:00,831 --> 00:03:06,693
THE DEMON WOULD DISINTEGRATE
AND THE SPELL BE EASILY BROKEN.

18
00:03:24,565 --> 00:03:26,931
BUT BEFORE THE ONE
BECAME COMPLETE,

19
00:03:26,965 --> 00:03:31,165
WERE YOU TRYING TO SEE
WHAT LAY BEYOND?

20
00:03:32,765 --> 00:03:35,598
- AND THERE YE WERE.

21
00:03:38,965 --> 00:03:43,698
YOUR DISGUISE IS
FINE...ONIGUMO.

22
00:03:44,965 --> 00:03:46,731
- HUH. ONIGUMO.

23
00:03:46,765 --> 00:03:48,331
NOW THAT BRINGS ME BACK.

24
00:03:48,365 --> 00:03:53,465
50 YEARS AGO, YOU SAVED ME,
TOOK PITY ON ME,

25
00:03:53,498 --> 00:03:56,798
AND SHELTERED THAT
FUGITIVE IN A CAVE.

26
00:03:56,831 --> 00:03:59,731
ONIGUMO OFFERED HIS BODY
TO THE DEMONS,

27
00:03:59,765 --> 00:04:02,598
WHO LATCHED ONTO HIS EVIL SOUL.

28
00:04:02,631 --> 00:04:06,498
AND THUS WAS BORN NARAKU.

29
00:04:08,465 --> 00:04:10,231
- THAT'S--

30
00:04:10,265 --> 00:04:11,398
- YES, INDEED.

31
00:04:11,431 --> 00:04:16,298
THE VERY THING YOU GAVE YOUR
LIFE TO ERASE FROM THIS WORLD.

32
00:04:16,331 --> 00:04:19,065
A SHARD OF THE SACRED JEWEL.

33
00:04:19,098 --> 00:04:21,698
- THEY SAY IT WAS
YOUR DESIRE TO POSSESS IT

34
00:04:21,731 --> 00:04:24,431
THAT BROUGHT YOU TO KILL ME.

35
00:04:24,965 --> 00:04:27,365
- DISCUSSING IT WITH ONE
WHO IS NO MORE

36
00:04:27,398 --> 00:04:30,631
THAN A COLLECTION OF
DEAD SOULS IS UNSEEMLY,

37
00:04:30,665 --> 00:04:36,031
BUT THE SEARCH FOR THE REMAINING
FRAGMENTS FRUSTRATES ME.

38
00:04:50,565 --> 00:04:54,631
THAT GIRL WHO WAS SO LIKE
AND YET UNLIKE YOU--

39
00:04:54,665 --> 00:04:58,631
A BATTLE BETWEEN THOSE
WHO CAN PURIFY EVIL.

40
00:04:58,665 --> 00:05:00,865
IF YOU YEARN FOR THIS WORLD,

41
00:05:00,898 --> 00:05:05,031
I BID YOU...GO AFTER HER.

42
00:05:14,898 --> 00:05:16,765
[BIRD CHIRPING]

43
00:05:16,798 --> 00:05:21,565
- WELL? WOULDN'T YOU SAY THOSE
TWO HAVE BEEN ACTING STRANGE?

44
00:05:21,598 --> 00:05:23,931
- YEP.

45
00:05:26,231 --> 00:05:27,565
- I...

46
00:05:27,598 --> 00:05:28,965
INUYASHA?

47
00:05:28,998 --> 00:05:31,565
HELLO!
- WHAT?

48
00:05:31,598 --> 00:05:33,631
- INUYASHA, LET'S GO.

49
00:05:33,665 --> 00:05:34,798
WE HAVE TO SAVE KIKYO.

50
00:05:34,831 --> 00:05:38,531
IT'S STILL EARLY.
THEY CAN'T HAVE GONE FAR.

51
00:05:39,165 --> 00:05:41,198
- I'LL SAVE HER ON MY OWN.

52
00:05:41,231 --> 00:05:43,831
- STOP BEING SUCH
A STUBBORN FOOL.

53
00:05:43,865 --> 00:05:44,798
- UGH!

54
00:05:44,831 --> 00:05:47,065
- YOU FORGOT WHO IT WAS
THAT KIDNAPPED KIKYO.

55
00:05:47,098 --> 00:05:48,531
I WANT MY OWN REVENGE.

56
00:05:48,565 --> 00:05:51,565
I WOULDN'T EVEN HAVE
THIS HOLE IN MY RIGHT HAND

57
00:05:51,598 --> 00:05:52,698
IF IT WEREN'T FOR NARAKU.

58
00:05:52,731 --> 00:05:55,465
- HE'S AN ENEMY
TO ALL OF US, REMEMBER?

59
00:05:55,498 --> 00:05:57,665
- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
YOU'RE SO SPECIAL?

60
00:05:57,698 --> 00:06:01,531
- LOOK, WE ALL KNOW WHAT
HAPPENED BETWEEN YOU AND KIKYO.

61
00:06:01,565 --> 00:06:02,731
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO SNEAK AROUND

62
00:06:02,765 --> 00:06:05,465
TRYING TO FIX EVERYTHING
BEHIND OUR BACKS.

63
00:06:05,498 --> 00:06:07,598
- I DON'T SNEAK AROUND, OK?

64
00:06:07,631 --> 00:06:09,231
I'VE NEVER SNUCK IN MY LIFE!

65
00:06:09,265 --> 00:06:12,631
- INUYASHA! OVER THERE!
- HUH?

66
00:06:12,665 --> 00:06:15,231
- IT'S KIKYO'S SOUL GATHERERS.

67
00:06:15,931 --> 00:06:18,565
- THEN SHE'S EVEN CLOSER
THAN WE THOUGHT.

68
00:06:18,598 --> 00:06:20,998
- YOU COMING?
- MM-HMM.

69
00:06:23,665 --> 00:06:26,331
- NOT THAT I'M COMPLAINING
OR ANYTHING, KAGOME,

70
00:06:26,365 --> 00:06:28,498
BUT WHY AREN'T YOU
WITH INUYASHA?

71
00:06:28,531 --> 00:06:30,931
- I, UM...UH...

72
00:06:30,965 --> 00:06:35,598
- BECAUSE RIGHT NOW,
HE ONLY CARES FOR KIKYO,
THAT'S WHY.

73
00:06:35,631 --> 00:06:39,031
BESIDES, WHY
HANG OFF HIM ANYWAY?

74
00:06:39,065 --> 00:06:41,698
HE'S NOT EVEN MY BOYFRIEND.

75
00:06:41,731 --> 00:06:42,431
[GASPS]

76
00:06:42,465 --> 00:06:44,765
OH, NO!
I THINK I'M BLUSHING!

77
00:06:44,798 --> 00:06:48,265
[GASPING]
I AM! I AM BLUSHING!

78
00:06:48,298 --> 00:06:50,331
- WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH KAGOME?

79
00:06:50,365 --> 00:06:52,665
- DON'T ASK ME.

80
00:06:53,331 --> 00:06:56,898
- KIKYO DIED
BECAUSE OF HIM.

81
00:06:58,998 --> 00:07:02,931
I WILL NOT LET NARAKU HAVE HER!

82
00:07:05,198 --> 00:07:07,598
- LOOK! MORE GATHERERS!

83
00:07:07,631 --> 00:07:10,131
[BUZZING]

84
00:07:10,165 --> 00:07:12,731
UH-OH.

85
00:07:16,998 --> 00:07:18,565
BUT THAT'S--

86
00:07:18,598 --> 00:07:20,465
LOOK OUT! IT'S A TRAP!

87
00:07:20,498 --> 00:07:22,565
- BE CAREFUL!

88
00:07:28,898 --> 00:07:31,431
- WHAT IS THAT UP THERE?

89
00:07:31,465 --> 00:07:33,365
I CAN'T--

90
00:07:33,398 --> 00:07:35,365
HUH?

91
00:07:37,131 --> 00:07:39,331
WHERE AM I?

92
00:07:42,898 --> 00:07:45,498
- THAT'S HIM!
THE ONE WHO ATTACKED US!

93
00:07:45,531 --> 00:07:47,765
- INUYASHA! IT'S INUYASHA!

94
00:07:47,798 --> 00:07:50,865
- THIS PLACE--
I DON'T KNOW WHERE I--

95
00:07:50,898 --> 00:07:52,698
[GASPS]

96
00:07:52,731 --> 00:07:54,165
IT CAN'T BE!

97
00:07:54,198 --> 00:07:56,898
THE SHIKON JEWEL!

98
00:07:56,931 --> 00:07:58,965
- INUYASHA!

99
00:07:58,998 --> 00:08:01,298
- HUH?

100
00:08:01,331 --> 00:08:03,498
AAH!

101
00:08:13,998 --> 00:08:17,698
K-KIKYO.

102
00:08:21,365 --> 00:08:24,531
OF COURSE!
IT'S 50 YEARS AGO.

103
00:08:24,565 --> 00:08:27,965
THE DAY KIKYO KILLED ME.

104
00:08:27,998 --> 00:08:29,931
AND THIS IS THE VILLAGE
WHERE I ATTACKED

105
00:08:29,965 --> 00:08:32,965
SO THAT I COULD STEAL
THE SACRED JEWEL.

106
00:08:32,998 --> 00:08:34,465
KIKYO, WAIT!

107
00:08:34,498 --> 00:08:36,065
IT WAS ALL JUST A TRAP!

108
00:08:36,098 --> 00:08:38,398
KIKYO, DON'T DO IT!

109
00:08:38,431 --> 00:08:40,865
KIKYO, NO!

110
00:08:40,898 --> 00:08:42,498
IS THIS HELL?

111
00:08:42,531 --> 00:08:44,031
IS IT A DREAM?

112
00:08:44,065 --> 00:08:46,831
HOW DID I GET HERE?

113
00:08:51,631 --> 00:08:53,498
- INUYASHA
AND THE OTHERS, GONE.

114
00:08:53,531 --> 00:08:58,031
HMM. AND THE WIND--
IT'S STARTING TO PICK UP.

115
00:08:59,731 --> 00:09:02,098
- IT'S SO CLOSE.

116
00:09:02,131 --> 00:09:04,198
TOO CLOSE.

117
00:09:07,031 --> 00:09:09,365
AAH!

118
00:09:12,831 --> 00:09:15,931
IT'S PULLING ME IN!

119
00:09:17,331 --> 00:09:18,265
- LOOK, KIRARA.

120
00:09:18,298 --> 00:09:19,998
SEE?
THERE'S NOBODY BEHIND US.

121
00:09:20,031 --> 00:09:25,365
HUH? WHAT'S WRONG?
WHY ARE YOU--AAH!

122
00:09:25,398 --> 00:09:26,265
HUH?

123
00:09:26,298 --> 00:09:27,831
WHERE'D KIRARA GO?

124
00:09:27,865 --> 00:09:32,298
WHAT? KAGOME!
SANGO! WAIT UP!

125
00:09:34,198 --> 00:09:36,998
THEY ALL LEFT THEIR CLOTHES.

126
00:09:37,031 --> 00:09:38,665
WHERE'D EVERYBODY GO?

127
00:09:38,698 --> 00:09:40,331
IF HERE'S WHERE
THEIR CLOTHES ARE,

128
00:09:40,365 --> 00:09:41,931
WHERE'D THE REST OF THEM GO?

129
00:09:41,965 --> 00:09:44,565
INUYASHA! MIROKU!

130
00:09:44,598 --> 00:09:47,865
OW! KAGOME! SANGO!

131
00:09:50,131 --> 00:09:52,198
[PANTING]

132
00:09:53,598 --> 00:09:55,198
- HUH?

133
00:10:03,298 --> 00:10:05,498
HUH?

134
00:10:16,631 --> 00:10:18,931
[WHIMPERS]

135
00:10:24,265 --> 00:10:26,165
AAH!

136
00:10:28,698 --> 00:10:30,698
KOHAKU?

137
00:10:39,798 --> 00:10:43,465
- THE EVIL SPELL
OF ILLUSORY DEATH.

138
00:10:43,498 --> 00:10:46,598
THE SOUL IS SUCH
A FRAGILE THING.

139
00:10:46,631 --> 00:10:52,165
SADNESS, FEAR, CONFUSION.

140
00:10:52,198 --> 00:10:54,465
IF EVEN SLIGHTEST DOUBT EXISTS

141
00:10:54,498 --> 00:10:57,765
AND IS TOUCHED BY
THE CREEPERS OF THIS WORLD,

142
00:10:57,798 --> 00:11:01,098
THAT SOUL WILL BE
CONSUMED WITH DARK.

143
00:11:01,131 --> 00:11:04,198
- WHERE CAN EVERYONE
HAVE GONE OFF TO?

144
00:11:04,231 --> 00:11:05,898
AAH!

145
00:11:05,931 --> 00:11:08,652
EW! WHAT'S THAT?

146
00:11:08,685 --> 00:11:11,666
AAH! AAH!

147
00:11:11,823 --> 00:11:14,423
- PERHAPS BECAUSE OF
THE JEWEL SHARDS,

148
00:11:14,456 --> 00:11:17,789
THAT GIRL ALONE
IS UNAFFECTED.

149
00:11:18,623 --> 00:11:20,889
ONLY SHE SHALL MAKE IT HERE.

150
00:11:20,923 --> 00:11:24,489
THE STAGE HAS BEEN
SET FOR YOU.

151
00:11:25,089 --> 00:11:28,156
- AREN'T YOU THE CLEVER ONE.

152
00:11:38,756 --> 00:11:41,456
- SO SHE'S DESTROYED
THE GOLLUM.

153
00:11:41,489 --> 00:11:44,623
HOW DARE SHE DEFY ME.

154
00:11:51,889 --> 00:11:53,523
- KIKYO.

155
00:11:54,556 --> 00:11:58,189
KIKYO! YOU'RE OK!
KIKYO!

156
00:12:04,023 --> 00:12:07,756
WE'VE BEEN...SO WORRIED
ABOUT YOU.

157
00:12:11,323 --> 00:12:13,289
[MOANS]

158
00:12:18,189 --> 00:12:19,123
AAH!

159
00:12:19,156 --> 00:12:21,823
[SCREAMS]

160
00:12:29,989 --> 00:12:32,323
[WHIMPERS]

161
00:12:38,023 --> 00:12:38,856
KIKYO.

162
00:12:38,889 --> 00:12:41,656
- NARAKU FINDS HIMSELF
FRIGHTENED OF YOU.

163
00:12:41,689 --> 00:12:44,989
HE TRIES TO CONTROL ME
WITH THE SACRED JEWEL,

164
00:12:45,023 --> 00:12:47,956
HOPING THAT I MIGHT BE
TURNED AGAINST YOU.

165
00:12:47,989 --> 00:12:51,156
- WILL SHE SAVE ME?

166
00:12:51,189 --> 00:12:52,923
[WHIMPERS]

167
00:12:58,589 --> 00:13:00,656
- THE JEWEL SHARD
IN YOUR CHEST!

168
00:13:00,689 --> 00:13:03,156
- SURELY THE PRIESTESS
WHO ONCE STOOD GUARD

169
00:13:03,189 --> 00:13:04,789
OVER THE SACRED JEWEL OF 4 SOULS

170
00:13:04,823 --> 00:13:10,256
HAS NOT FALLEN SO LOW AS TO BE
CONTROLLED BY A MERE SHARD.

171
00:13:15,223 --> 00:13:17,189
- OH!

172
00:13:35,823 --> 00:13:38,223
[WINCES AND GROANS]

173
00:13:38,256 --> 00:13:40,756
- KIKYO!

174
00:13:42,056 --> 00:13:44,223
[WINCES]

175
00:13:49,089 --> 00:13:53,989
- SHE CAME TO ME IN
HER PAIN, ALL ALONE.

176
00:13:54,023 --> 00:13:58,156
KIKYO, YOU'LL NEVER
BE ALONE AGAIN.

177
00:13:58,823 --> 00:14:03,356
I SWEAR IT.
I WILL ALWAYS PROTECT YOU.

178
00:14:05,623 --> 00:14:06,823
HUH?

179
00:14:06,856 --> 00:14:07,789
BUT I DON'T--

180
00:14:07,823 --> 00:14:11,223
YOU MEAN THERE'S SOMEONE
ELSE I SHOULD PROTECT?

181
00:14:15,056 --> 00:14:16,123
WHO, THOUGH?

182
00:14:16,156 --> 00:14:20,189
WHO'S THIS OTHER PERSON
I'M SUPPOSED TO--

183
00:14:26,756 --> 00:14:28,089
KAGOME.

184
00:14:28,123 --> 00:14:30,856
OF COURSE!
HOW THE HECK COULD I HAVE--

185
00:14:30,889 --> 00:14:33,023
WHERE'S KAGOME?
TELL ME!

186
00:14:33,056 --> 00:14:33,989
- INUYASHA!

187
00:14:34,023 --> 00:14:38,456
IS SHE MORE IMPORTANT
TO YOU THAN I AM?

188
00:14:38,489 --> 00:14:41,689
- IT'S ALL BEEN
AN ILLUSION, HASN'T IT?

189
00:14:46,523 --> 00:14:49,023
- AAH!
- MIROKU!

190
00:14:49,056 --> 00:14:52,556
- AAH!

191
00:14:52,589 --> 00:14:54,689
[WHIMPERING]

192
00:15:02,089 --> 00:15:04,623
- MIROKU!

193
00:15:08,856 --> 00:15:09,856
AHH!

194
00:15:09,889 --> 00:15:11,423
HEY, ARE YOU OK?

195
00:15:11,456 --> 00:15:14,523
- MY--MY--
THE WIND TUNNEL--I--

196
00:15:14,556 --> 00:15:16,923
- HE'S SCARED.
REALLY SCARED.

197
00:15:16,956 --> 00:15:20,123
- WAKE UP! SNAP OUT OF IT!

198
00:15:21,456 --> 00:15:24,223
- IT WAS SWALLOWING UP
MY ENTIRE BODY.

199
00:15:24,256 --> 00:15:26,089
- IT'S THAT TREE,
THOSE ROOTS.

200
00:15:26,123 --> 00:15:28,456
- QUICK! YOU GOT TO
FIND SANGO AND SHIPPO.

201
00:15:28,489 --> 00:15:32,556
BET YOU ANYTHING
THEY'RE UNDER THE SAME
SPELL THAT GOT YOU AND ME.

202
00:15:32,589 --> 00:15:35,223
I GOT TO GO FIND KAGOME.

203
00:15:35,256 --> 00:15:39,256
KAGOME! WHERE ARE YOU?

204
00:15:52,366 --> 00:15:54,107
KAGOME!

205
00:15:56,795 --> 00:15:58,376
KAGOME!

206
00:16:01,182 --> 00:16:03,443
- INUYASHA.

207
00:16:04,795 --> 00:16:05,695
- KAGOME!

208
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:08,983
THOSE ROOTS CAUSED
SOME KIND OF AN ILLUSION.

209
00:16:09,016 --> 00:16:12,716
SEEMS LIKE YOU GOT AWAY
FROM IT OK, THOUGH.

210
00:16:13,416 --> 00:16:16,750
- UH...UH...

211
00:16:20,516 --> 00:16:22,116
UH...
- HUH?

212
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:23,983
[GASPS]
HUH?

213
00:16:24,016 --> 00:16:26,050
KIKYO!

214
00:16:26,083 --> 00:16:29,483
THOSE ARE KAGOME'S
JEWEL SHARDS!

215
00:16:31,383 --> 00:16:32,983
KAGOME.

216
00:16:33,016 --> 00:16:35,683
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

217
00:16:37,783 --> 00:16:39,083
YOU DIDN'T!

218
00:16:39,116 --> 00:16:40,783
DON'T TELL ME IT WAS YOU!

219
00:16:40,816 --> 00:16:42,683
- WHAT'S WRONG, INUYASHA?

220
00:16:42,716 --> 00:16:44,083
TELL ME--
WHY IS IT I FEEL

221
00:16:44,116 --> 00:16:46,116
THAT YOU'RE UNHAPPY
TO KNOW I'M WELL?

222
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:49,350
- ANSWER ME!
JUST WHAT DID YOU DO TO HER?

223
00:16:49,383 --> 00:16:50,850
- I TRIED TO KILL HER.

224
00:16:50,883 --> 00:16:53,783
WHAT IS IT THAT YOU PLAN
TO DO ABOUT IT?

225
00:16:53,816 --> 00:16:56,650
WILL YOU KILL ME?

226
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:59,150
[GROWLING]

227
00:16:59,183 --> 00:17:02,450
TELL ME--WHEN NARAKU
HAD YOU UNDER HIS SPELL,

228
00:17:02,483 --> 00:17:05,383
WHAT WAS IT THAT
YOU THOUGHT ABOUT?

229
00:17:05,416 --> 00:17:06,583
[SIGHS]

230
00:17:06,616 --> 00:17:12,616
- I...I SWEAR I'LL
ALWAYS PROTECT YOU.

231
00:17:12,650 --> 00:17:14,883
[SNICKERS]

232
00:17:14,916 --> 00:17:17,550
[LAUGHS]

233
00:17:17,583 --> 00:17:22,216
- NOW, COULD YOU HAVE SAID THAT
IF YOU WERE GOING TO KILL ME?

234
00:17:28,116 --> 00:17:30,050
EMBRACING DEATH TOGETHER--

235
00:17:30,083 --> 00:17:33,150
NOW THAT'S A DAY I'LL WAIT FOR.

236
00:17:47,383 --> 00:17:51,350
- KAGOME, TELL ME
WHAT SHE DID TO YOU.

237
00:17:51,383 --> 00:17:54,850
- SHE TOOK THE SACRED
JEWEL BACK FROM ME.

238
00:17:54,883 --> 00:17:56,150
I'M SORRY.

239
00:17:56,183 --> 00:17:57,950
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I'M ASKING!

240
00:17:57,983 --> 00:17:59,883
DID KIKYO REALLY TRY TO--

241
00:17:59,916 --> 00:18:01,583
- THEN DON'T ASK ME!

242
00:18:01,616 --> 00:18:03,083
[GASPS]

243
00:18:03,116 --> 00:18:04,983
- KAGOME.

244
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:07,650
I CAN'T DO IT.

245
00:18:07,683 --> 00:18:10,650
I FEEL LIKE
I'M TELLING ON HER.

246
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:15,916
- SO, UH...ARE YOU TWO
FINISHED TALKING?

247
00:18:17,316 --> 00:18:22,883
- [VOICE-OVER]
TO KIKYO, MY LIFE...
IT HAS NO MEANING.

248
00:18:22,916 --> 00:18:25,683
- THOSE ROOTS CAUSED
SOME KIND OF AN ILLUSION.

249
00:18:25,716 --> 00:18:29,683
SEEMS LIKE YOU GOT AWAY
FROM IT OK, THOUGH.

250
00:18:29,716 --> 00:18:32,483
- UH...UH...

251
00:18:32,516 --> 00:18:34,116
- [VOICE-OVER]
THE ILLUSORY DEATH.

252
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:38,050
OUR PAIN AND CONFUSION
PUT US ALL TO THE TEST.

253
00:18:38,083 --> 00:18:38,950
MINE, TOO.

254
00:18:38,983 --> 00:18:42,350
IT GAVE ME A SMALL LOOK
INTO MY OWN HEART.

255
00:18:44,950 --> 00:18:47,350
INTO A PLACE WHERE...

256
00:18:47,383 --> 00:18:49,950
INUYASHA AND KIKYO WERE...

257
00:18:49,983 --> 00:18:52,850
IN LOVE WITH EACH OTHER.

258
00:19:00,083 --> 00:19:02,350
[WIND HOWLING]

259
00:19:14,950 --> 00:19:18,683
- YOU'RE CARELESS, NARAKU.

260
00:19:18,716 --> 00:19:19,783
- SO, KIKYO?

261
00:19:19,816 --> 00:19:24,050
- ONCE YOUR LITTLE POPPET
IS BROKEN, YOU SEE NOTHING.

262
00:19:24,083 --> 00:19:25,116
REMEMBER THAT.

263
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:29,450
YOUR PETTY FEATS OF MINOR
SORCERY CAN NOT AFFECT ME.

264
00:19:29,483 --> 00:19:31,850
AS FOR THE BARRIER
AROUND THE CASTLE,

265
00:19:31,883 --> 00:19:34,583
THE ONE YOU ERECTED
TO KEEP OUT INUYASHA,

266
00:19:34,616 --> 00:19:37,950
THAT WAS EASY ENOUGH
FOR ME TO BREAK.

267
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:49,516
YOU WANTED IT, DIDN'T YOU?

268
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:52,883
I LEAVE IT TO YOU
TO STAND GUARD OVER.

269
00:19:52,916 --> 00:19:56,183
AFTER ALL, WHO NEEDS
ITS POWER MORE THAN YOU?

270
00:19:56,216 --> 00:20:00,350
AND YOU DO NEED IT, DON'T YOU?

271
00:20:00,383 --> 00:20:02,283
DEMON NARAKU?

272
00:20:02,316 --> 00:20:04,883
OR IS IT...

273
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:08,283
HALF-DEMON NARAKU?

274
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:12,583
- A MERE HALF-DEMON,
I, NARAKU?

275
00:20:12,616 --> 00:20:15,116
- TRUE, YOU DISGUISED
YOURSELF WELL,

276
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:17,250
BUT YOU'RE STILL
THAT FUGITIVE HUMAN,

277
00:20:17,283 --> 00:20:22,250
AND THE BLOOD OF WHO YOU
ONCE WERE CAN NEVER BE ERASED.

278
00:20:24,083 --> 00:20:25,616
YOU SEEK THE SACRED JEWEL

279
00:20:25,650 --> 00:20:29,783
TO BECOME A FULL-FLEDGED
DEMON, DO YOU NOT?

280
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:33,816
- IF SO, WHY GIVE ME THE SHARDS?

281
00:20:34,193 --> 00:20:40,171
AM I NOT THE ONE YOU SEEK TO
AVENGE YOUR DEATH 50 YEARS AGO?

282
00:20:40,850 --> 00:20:44,550
- HA HA! IT WAS ONLY
MY BODY THAT DIED.

283
00:20:44,583 --> 00:20:46,416
I MAY HAVE LEFT IT
BEHIND THAT DAY,

284
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:49,583
BUT WITH THIS NEW ONE,
I'M EVEN STRONGER.

285
00:20:49,616 --> 00:20:53,183
I DON'T ASK THAT
YOU UNDERSTAND.

286
00:20:55,950 --> 00:20:58,316
I'M RETURNING TO THE TEMPLE.

287
00:20:58,350 --> 00:21:00,216
I WILL NEITHER RUN NOR HIDE.

288
00:21:00,250 --> 00:21:03,883
SEND A MESSENGER
IF YOU NEED ME.

289
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:15,716
- IT'S APPEARED AGAIN.

290
00:21:16,683 --> 00:21:19,544
NO MATTER HOW OFTEN
I CHANGE FLESH,

291
00:21:19,578 --> 00:21:24,659
THE BURN SCARS OF THE FUGITIVE
ONIGUMO WILL NOT LEAVE MY BACK.

292
00:21:29,992 --> 00:21:31,225
- GO, NARAKU.

293
00:21:31,422 --> 00:21:35,422
GATHER THE SHARDS OF THE JEWEL,
AND ONCE YOU'VE FOUND THEM ALL,

294
00:21:35,456 --> 00:21:38,856
THEN I WILL SEND YOU TO HELL.

295
00:21:43,256 --> 00:21:44,689
I'M FREE TO HATE.

296
00:21:45,182 --> 00:21:49,649
MY SOUL IS SO MUCH FREER NOW
THAN IT WAS THEN.

297
00:21:51,049 --> 00:21:56,482
FREE TO HATE...
FREE TO LOVE.

298
00:22:06,182 --> 00:22:08,916
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

299
00:23:39,001 --> 00:23:40,401
- [VOICE-OVER]
OH, GREAT!

300
00:23:40,435 --> 00:23:42,535
MY SACRED JEWEL'S BEEN STOLEN.

301
00:23:42,568 --> 00:23:44,101
NOW I CAN'T GO BACK HOME.

302
00:23:44,135 --> 00:23:46,035
LEND ME YOURS,
MIROKU, PLEASE?

303
00:23:46,068 --> 00:23:48,701
I NEED TO GO BACK HOME
FOR MY TEST TOMORROW.

304
00:23:48,735 --> 00:23:51,435
WHAT?
OH, SANGO, YOU WILL?

305
00:23:51,468 --> 00:23:54,301
THANK YOU SO MUCH!

306
00:23:54,335 --> 00:23:55,935
UH, MYOGA?

307
00:23:55,968 --> 00:23:56,901
WHO'S THAT?

308
00:23:56,935 --> 00:23:59,501
THE MAN WHO MADE TETSUSAIGA?

309
00:23:59,535 --> 00:24:02,101
NEXT TIME,
"TETSUSAIGA AND TENSEIGA."

310
00:24:02,135 --> 00:24:03,135
SEE YOU SOON!

